### ê·¸ë˜í”„ êµ¬ì¡°
```
CVE
â”œâ”€[:AFFECTS]â†’ CPE â†[:HAS_VERSION]â”€ Product â†[:PRODUCES]â”€ Vendor
â”œâ”€[:HAS_WEAKNESS]â†’ CWE
â”œâ”€[:HAS_REFERENCE]â†’ Reference
â”œâ”€[:HAS_EXPLOIT]â†’ Exploit
